{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Planica up close","content":"<p><em>Wake up! Wake up, we&#8217;re gonna be late!</em></p>\n<div style=\"width: 352px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><img class=\"  \" title=\"Planica\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/fa00e838704a11e18bb812313804a181_72.jpg\" alt=\"Planica\" width=\"342\" height=\"342\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Planica</p></div>\n<p>5am.</p>\n<p>Took my sister to <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Planica\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?ll=46.4983333333,13.7391666667&amp;spn=0.1,0.1&amp;q=46.4983333333,13.7391666667 (Planica)&amp;t=h\" rel=\"geolocation\">Planica</a> to watch a bunch of <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Flying squirrel\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flying_squirrel\" rel=\"wikipedia\">flying squirrel</a> men throw themselves off a big hill with long sticks attached to their feet to see who can go the farthest. All the while suffering a bunch of loud drunkish people.</p>\n<p>At least that&#8217;s what I thought &#8230; but all in all it was actually pretty damn awesome!</p>\n<p>The two free tickets didn&#8217;t just get us in the event place, after some careful maneuvering by The Ticket Guy we also got into the VIP section, right under the landing spot, with a good view of the whole flight.</p>\n<p>Then the VIP section turned into the <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Very Important Person\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Very_Important_Person\" rel=\"wikipedia\">VIP seats</a>, the ones closest to all the action.</p>\n<p>Then it became a trip up the hill to see everything <em>very</em>Â up close.</p>\n<p>Even the judge&#8217;s house thingy.</p>\n<p>I will never forget the eery calm of standing right next to the slope and having a guy <em>fall</em> past you, into nothing, seemingly laying on air. Subtle whoosh sound. Amazing.</p>\n<p>And the speed on the take off ramp! Wow! TV doesn&#8217;t do it justice <em>at all</em>. Yeah, sure, he&#8217;s doing 104km/h, so what? But when you&#8217;re standing 10 meters away &#8230; damn. Those guys are wearing underpants with a lot more room than mine have &#8230;</p>\n<p>Seeing <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Robert Kranjec\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Kranjec\" rel=\"wikipedia\">Robert Kranjec</a> jump a 231m was &#8230; impressive. The landing looks much harder in real life than it does on the telly.</p>\n<p>Alas, the <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"IPhone\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IPhone\" rel=\"wikipedia\">iPhone</a> camera was too slow to catch anyone in the air.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_4000\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-3.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4000 \" title=\"Looking up from down below\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-3-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Looking up from down below\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-3-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-3-300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Looking up from down below</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_3998\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-1.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-3998 \" title=\"A bad crowd shot\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-1-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"A bad crowd shot\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-1-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-1-300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">A bad crowd shot</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_3997\" style=\"width: 545px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-3997 \" title=\"There was a guy in a full deer suit\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-764x1024.jpg\" alt=\"There was a guy in a full deer suit\" width=\"535\" height=\"717\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-764x1024.jpg 764w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">There was a guy in a full deer suit</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_3999\" style=\"width: 727px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-2.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-3999 \" title=\"Plenty of balloons behind the VIP area\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-2-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"Plenty of balloons behind the VIP area\" width=\"717\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-2-1024x764.jpg 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-2-300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Plenty of balloons behind the VIP area</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4002\" style=\"width: 545px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-5.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4002 \" title=\"Ski lifts are weird without snow\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-5-764x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Ski lifts are weird without snow\" width=\"535\" height=\"717\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-5-764x1024.jpg 764w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-5-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ski lifts are weird without snow</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4001\" style=\"width: 545px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-4.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4001 \" title=\"Planica's baby sibling\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-4-764x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Planica's baby sibling\" width=\"535\" height=\"717\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-4-764x1024.jpg 764w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-4-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Planica&#39;s baby sibling</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4003\" style=\"width: 545px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-6.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4003 \" title=\"The crowd below\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-6-764x1024.jpg\" alt=\"The crowd below\" width=\"535\" height=\"717\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-6-764x1024.jpg 764w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-6-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">The crowd below</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4005\" style=\"width: 545px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-8.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4005 \" title=\"Whoosh, gone\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-8-764x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Whoosh, gone\" width=\"535\" height=\"717\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-8-764x1024.jpg 764w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-8-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Whoosh, gone</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4004\" style=\"width: 545px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-7.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4004 \" title=\"Best seats?\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-7-764x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Best seats?\" width=\"535\" height=\"717\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-7-764x1024.jpg 764w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/photo-7-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Best seats?</p></div>\n<div class=\"zemanta-pixie\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; height: 15px;\"><a class=\"zemanta-pixie-a\" title=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\" href=\"http://www.zemanta.com/\"><img class=\"zemanta-pixie-img\" style=\"border: none; float: right;\" src=\"http://img.zemanta.com/zemified_e.png?x-id=08a8cb04-5478-47d3-bd8a-9f93f6dca18d\" alt=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\" /></a></div>\n"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Swizec Blog","subtitle":"Fetch Data From Local WP Install"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"adac44d1-79af-5eed-b312-2324088cf3df"}}